The path is muddy.

00:34:36.639 --> 00:34:37.800
Let the horses rest.

00:34:44.639 --> 00:34:45.480
Wait.

00:34:55.320 --> 00:34:56.840
These hoof prints are unusual.

00:34:58.079 --> 00:35:00.519
This is considered a key route.

00:35:00.880 --> 00:35:04.639
Seeing hoof prints on the ground
should be usual.

00:35:06.480 --> 00:35:07.119
No.

00:35:14.000 --> 00:35:15.960
These are Tianlong Cult's
distinctive horseshoes.

00:35:17.880 --> 00:35:18.760
They're here.

00:35:30.159 --> 00:35:31.360
I've heard about it.

00:35:31.719 --> 00:35:33.360
On the way back last time,

00:35:33.480 --> 00:35:34.440
Tang

00:35:34.800 --> 00:35:36.800
(Linglong Sect, Sect Leader Shi)
ran into Long Zhentian head-on.

00:35:37.360 --> 00:35:39.119
(Youyou Sect, Qiao, Langya Sect, Lu)
Who knows what happened?

00:35:39.119 --> 00:35:39.800
Could it be

00:35:40.639 --> 00:35:41.440
nothing's left?

00:35:41.440 --> 00:35:42.480
Don't talk nonsense.

00:35:42.559 --> 00:35:44.440
(Qinghe Sect Leader Ye)
Sect Leader Tang is experienced.

00:35:44.840 --> 00:35:46.039
If they do meet,

00:35:46.199 --> 00:35:48.119
Long Zhentian will likely suffer.

00:35:50.679 --> 00:35:53.440
If nothing happens, he should appear.

00:35:53.599 --> 00:35:55.280
Look at the time.

00:35:55.599 --> 00:35:56.320
No more waiting.

00:35:56.679 --> 00:35:57.519
We're here.

00:35:59.559 --> 00:36:01.559
Cangqiong Sect disciple, Chun Ge.

00:36:01.599 --> 00:36:02.119
Min.

00:36:02.239 --> 00:36:03.559
- Greetings.
- Greetings.

