If they cause trouble
on Zongyu Mountain,

00:36:49.920 --> 00:36:51.800
I'll make sure they go back dead.

00:36:52.480 --> 00:36:53.239
Sect Leader Lu.

00:36:53.400 --> 00:36:54.960
